		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>A hellcaller has entered into a pact with dark powers, most often with &amp;reference[fiend]{Fiends} or their ilk. The patron typically requires that a warlock does some specific dark deed before receiving their first powers.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Hellcaller</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.O1owFjLB6wfrqs0J]{Dark One's Blessing}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.oYk90ubP0YAciMKr]{Dark One's Own Luck}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.F1ybwcvPGQeZeJkH]{Fiendish Resilience}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.mHPM9z4TIVNJwfJ7]{Hurl Through Hell}</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption><p>Expanded Spell List</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p><strong>Warlock Level</strong></p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p><strong>Extra Spells</strong></p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.etJoWZwBdvTMuJwh]{Burning Hands}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.xwb82OAnypYUZ5BO]{Command}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.56KyqRJhW1cM3JaF]{Blindness/Deafness}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Ggy29O9qIiYJTo1c]{Scorching Ray}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>5</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.pbT9cw6nsjpmwrVZ]{Fireball}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.14B8dD9iTLSb2nRc]{Stinking Cloud}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>7</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.IXTamgZ9OiDPEu0v]{Fire Shield}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.zQ7lBRzId8peTjor]{Wall of Fire}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>9</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.JMvciQxc508dJ3t8]{Dominate}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.TM7nuwiFhBjdE2MT]{Hallow}</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
